  "description": "<ul><li>Automotive Company</li><li><strong>Basic up to $3,000</strong></li><li><strong>5.125 days | 9:00 AM – 6:15 PM</strong></li><li><strong>Location: Alexandra Road </strong></li><li>Walking distance from MRT Queenstown & Redhill</li><li>Contract: 1-year, renewable</li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide administrative and sales support for motor and general insurance</li><li>Liaise with insurance companies, customers, and internal teams for quotations, renewals, and policy issuance</li><li>Prepare, process, and maintain accurate insurance documentation and system recordsHandle customer enquiries via email and phone</li><li>Ensure compliance with industry standards and company procedures</li></ul><p><br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘O’ Level; At least 2 years of relevant experience in insurance or related field</li><li>General Insurance Certificate (BCP / ComGI / PGI) is an advantage</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>For consideration, kindly submit your CV by clicking “APPLY\nNOW”<br /></p><p><em>Only shortlisted candidates would be notified</em>*<br /></p><p>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | 15C7752</p><p>R24124448 | Nana Yeoh Li Xuan</p>",
